name: Chipotle Shrimp Wrap
description: A cold wrap stuffed with chipotle shrimp, quinoa black beans, tomatoes, corn, onion, and avocado tossed with a mildly-spiced aioli in a flour tortilla. Served with a fruit cup and a square of Ghiradelli chocolate.
reviews: lots of good flavor, juicy. Shrimp was tasty and the overall wrap was great. Would get it again!
One of the best things I've had at eat club
